name: Nor the light
description: The great Global Mind. It maintains everything and has everything, for your pomp and for your misfortune, the Mind opens and obstructs you depending on your decrees, when you play a musical note it does not travel alone, it travels thanks to a great mechanism of refined perfection that transforms that note in a divine sound. We call it God or Great Mystery, but it has no name or cradle, it just exists.
